OL,5, Links between Boris Johnson and BBC    
OL,6, chairman Richard Sharp are under fresh 
OL,7, scrutiny, following a report that the  
OL,8, then-prime minister was told to stop   
OL,9, asking Mr Sharp for financial "advice".
OL,11,FMr Sharp's appointment is under review 
OL,12,Ffollowing successive reports in the    
OL,13,FSunday Times that he helped Mr Johnson 
OL,14,Fsecure a loan before getting his job.  
OL,16,FThe paper's latest story cites a leaked
OL,17,FCabinet Office memo from December 2020.
OL,18,FOfficials have declined to comment.    
OL,20,FBoth men deny any wrongdoing.          
